com.jakubpetriska.gameengine.api.components

Class Transform

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jakubpetriska.gameengine.api.Component
      • com.jakubpetriska.gameengine.api.components.Transform

  • public class Transform
extends Component
    Holds transformation of a GameObject.

    Transformation is relative to parent GameObject. World (absolute) transformation can be obtained using appropriate methods.

    • Constructor Detail

      • Transform

        public Transform()
        Create new transformation.

        Newly created transformation is identity. It has 0 translation, 0 rotation and scale of 1 in all axes.

        public void translateBy(float x,
                        float y,
                        float z)
        Translate this transform by given amount in direction of each axis.

        The axes along which the transformation is translated are transformed by this transformation.

        Parameters:
        x - Amount of translation in the direction of X axis.
        y - Amount of translation in the direction of Y axis.
        z - Amount of translation in the direction of Z axis.
